      <title>特朗普希望总统对美联储政策有“发言权”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/trump-wants-presidents-to-have-some-say-over-fed-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普表示，总统应该对利率和货币政策有“一些发言权”，此举违背了美联储长期以来独立于政治参与者的惯例。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/trump-wants-presidents-to-have-some-say-over-fed-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 19:22:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉因与奥尔特加发生争执将驱逐尼加拉瓜大使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/lula-to-expel-nicaraguan-ambassador-amid-dispute-with-ortega</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦将驱逐尼加拉瓜驻巴西大使，这将加深这位左翼领导人与传统盟友丹尼尔·奥尔特加之间的裂痕。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/lula-to-expel-nicaraguan-ambassador-amid-dispute-with-ortega</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 19:13:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克总统任命总理取代财政部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/mozambique-president-replaces-finance-head-with-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克总统府周四在一份声明中表示，总统菲利佩·纽西任命总理阿德里亚诺·马莱亚内取代财政部长马克斯·托内拉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/mozambique-president-replaces-finance-head-with-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 19:08:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普与哈里斯展开辩论，力图重塑竞选格局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/trump-proposes-three-debates-with-harris-in-bid-to-reshape-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党候选人唐纳德·特朗普在新闻发布会上提议与副总统卡马拉·哈里斯进行三场辩论，他希望重新获得最近几天被其 2024 年新对手所掩盖的竞选势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/trump-proposes-three-debates-with-harris-in-bid-to-reshape-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 18:26:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>F-22 战机抵达中东，表明美国支持以色列</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/f-22-jets-arrive-in-the-mideast-to-signal-us-support-for-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在哈马斯高层领导人被暗杀后，美国空军的隐形 F-22 猛禽战机抵达中东，进行武力展示，旨在阻止伊朗及其代理人袭击以色列。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/f-22-jets-arrive-in-the-mideast-to-signal-us-support-for-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 17:12:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果当选总统，加纳巴武米亚将把塞地与黄金挂钩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/ghana-s-bawumia-to-link-cedi-to-gold-if-elected-president-lzljaq5j</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳副总统马哈穆杜·巴武米亚 (Mahamudu Bawumia) 表示，如果他在 12 月赢得总统大选，他将采用将塞地货币与黄金挂钩的新汇率制度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/ghana-s-bawumia-to-link-cedi-to-gold-if-elected-president-lzljaq5j</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 17:10:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
